196
00:10:19,830 --> 00:10:21,290
with my wife and children.

197
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,200
You didn't win fairly.

198
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:50,440
There were three of you fighting against me alone!

199
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,950
There were three of you too!

200
00:10:51,950 --> 00:10:52,990
And you ambushed us.

201
00:10:52,990 --> 00:10:53,590
Moreover,

202
00:10:53,770 --> 00:10:55,500
he was not using a handy weapon.

203
00:10:56,190 --> 00:10:58,250
Then let's fight with handy weapons.

204
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,670
Just you wait.

205
00:11:06,730 --> 00:11:08,590
This fake sheriff is so arrogant.

206
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:10,120
Teach him a good lesson.

207
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:11,590
