215
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:22,550
I was originally from a decent family

216
00:12:22,550 --> 00:12:24,150
in Yunding County, Hanzhou.

217
00:12:24,430 --> 00:12:26,670
My family made a living by making wine.

218
00:12:27,230 --> 00:12:28,230
Twenty years ago,

219
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:30,710
we encountered a corrupt and tyrannical sheriff who

220
00:12:30,710 --> 00:12:32,570
imposed all sorts of harsh taxes,

221
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:33,430
making it

222
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:35,520
hard for us to make a living.

223
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,340
My father

224
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:40,910
was forced to the point of coughing blood and died.

225
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:42,740
I wanted to avenge him,

226
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:43,790
so I became an apprentice to learn martial arts,

227
00:12:43,790 --> 00:12:45,650
which took me ten years to master.

228
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:46,570
Unexpectedly,

229
00:12:46,830 --> 00:12:48,310
that sheriff had already been promoted

230
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:49,750
and went off somewhere else

231
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:51,070
to make a fortune.

232
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:54,680
I took over my father's wine making business,

233
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,760
got married, and had children.

234
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:58,820
We had a few good years.

235
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,110
Then,

236
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:01,890
another sheriff came,

237
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:04,240
who was even more corrupt and tyrannical

238
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:05,030
than the one

239
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:06,590
who drove my father to death.

240
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:07,830
I had a quarrel with him,

241
00:13:07,830 --> 00:13:09,420
then I was thrown into prison.

242
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:10,470
He even wanted to seize

243
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:12,190
our family's ancestral wine cellar.

244
00:13:12,190 --> 00:13:13,810
My wife went to plead with him,

245
00:13:13,810 --> 00:13:15,540
but he attempted to harass her.

246
00:13:15,910 --> 00:13:17,350
Unable to bear the humiliation,

247
00:13:17,350 --> 00:13:18,350
she took our child

248
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,150
and jumped into the river

249
00:13:25,830 --> 00:13:27,670
After receiving the news in prison,

250
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:29,510
I managed to break out

251
00:13:29,990 --> 00:13:31,050
and nearly beat him

252
00:13:31,860 --> 00:13:32,860
to death.

253
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,400
Then why

254
00:13:35,430 --> 00:13:36,560
didn't you kill him?

255
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:39,630
Despite my ten years of martial arts training,

256
00:13:39,630 --> 00:13:41,090
I had never killed anyone.

257
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:44,390
Seeing that corrupt sheriff living in luxury,

258
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:45,590
I was filled with rage

259
00:13:45,870 --> 00:13:47,070
and robbed him clean.

260
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:48,570
Since then,

261
00:13:49,350 --> 00:13:51,080
I've been wandering in Jianghu

262
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:54,020
and met these two brothers.

263
00:13:55,430 --> 00:13:57,070
Their experiences are pretty much

264
00:13:57,070 --> 00:13:58,390
the same as mine.

265
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:01,050
All three of us despise

266
00:14:01,230 --> 00:14:03,150
sheriffs who impose heavy taxes and extort money from the people.

267
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,340
So wherever we go,

268
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:06,280
we steal everything

269
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:08,350
from the sheriff's household.

270
00:14:08,350 --> 00:14:08,990
However,

271
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:11,720
the sheriff of Shen County is quite clean.

272
00:14:12,150 --> 00:14:14,150
There is no illicit gain at his home at all.

273
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:15,480
I heard he's a young man.

274
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:17,400
I'd really like to meet him.

275
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:21,850
Can having no illicit gain at home

276
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:23,520
prove he's a good official?

277
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,550
I've inquired about it.

278
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:27,270
Last year, there was a locust plague

279
00:14:27,270 --> 00:14:29,330
and many fields had no harvest at all.

280
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:31,110
This young sheriff

281
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:33,800
spent all his own money on disaster relief.

282
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,330
Isn't that a good official?

283
00:14:36,260 --> 00:14:37,020
Alright.

284
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:39,770
Enough talking about others.

285
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:41,000
Let's talk about you now.

286
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,810
Why were you heading to Chang'an

287
00:14:42,830 --> 00:14:44,040
in the name of the sheriff

288
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,150
of Wannian County?

289
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,740
I heard that

290
00:14:50,310 --> 00:14:52,100
there are sheriffs in the capital too.

291
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:54,630
