00:14:56,670 --> 00:14:57,510
Indeed.

294
00:14:57,700 --> 00:14:59,320
Daring to impersonate a sheriff?

295
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,640
The moment I walked in,

296
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:02,030
I could tell he was up to no good.

297
00:15:02,030 --> 00:15:02,630
Everyone,

298
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:03,550
now you know

299
00:15:03,570 --> 00:15:05,030
I've been wrongly accused, right?

300
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:06,830
Hurry up and untie me!

301
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:09,030
Though you didn't kill him,

302
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:11,310
the stolen goods are right here.

303
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:14,750
You can't say you were wrongly accused of theft, can you?

304
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:16,870
A bit of pilfering on a journey

305
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:18,260
is understandable.

306
00:15:20,070 --> 00:15:21,530
You really are shameless.

307
00:15:21,550 --> 00:15:23,120
Why are you, a young girl,

308
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:23,750
so fierce?

309
00:15:24,110 --> 00:15:25,390
Daring to contend with men,

310
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:27,190
you'll never get married.

311
00:15:27,430 --> 00:15:29,590
My marriage is not your concern.

312
00:15:29,730 --> 00:15:31,000
I'll cut out your tongue first!

313
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:31,530
Yingtao!

314
00:15:35,190 --> 00:15:36,590
The fake sheriff Long Tai

315
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:37,870
and his two accomplices

316
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,000
have been captured.

317
00:15:39,110 --> 00:15:41,150
However, the true murderer of Mi Tuo

318
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:42,890
has not been found yet.

319
00:15:43,990 --> 00:15:44,870
Who do you think

320
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:46,960
is the most suspicious?

321
00:15:48,230 --> 00:15:49,300
It's not me anyway.

322
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:50,910
Nor me.

323
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:52,050
Since

324
00:15:52,370 --> 00:15:55,200
the fake sheriff has been exposed,

325
00:15:55,230 --> 00:15:56,500
the real sheriff

326
00:15:57,190 --> 00:15:59,080
should stop hiding.

327
00:16:03,710 --> 00:16:04,350
Could it be

328
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:07,030
that Mr. Lu is the sheriff?

329
00:16:11,070 --> 00:16:12,230
I'm Lu Lingfeng,

330
00:16:14,310 --> 00:16:17,440
on my way to take office as the sheriff of Yunding County.

331
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:26,830
Long Tai,

332
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:27,600
remember.

333
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:29,560
After I take office in Yunding,

334
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:31,430
I will definitely not arbitrarily collect harsh taxes and levies.

335
00:16:31,430 --> 00:16:33,290
As for those old and unjust cases,

336
00:16:33,310 --> 00:16:35,240
I will investigate them one by one.

337
00:16:37,310 --> 00:16:38,270
If that's true,

338
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:40,890
it will be a blessing for Yunding.

339
00:16:44,030 --> 00:16:45,630
Hermit and Swordsman,

340
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:48,230
keep an eye on these people

341
00:16:48,870 --> 00:16:49,470
while I

342
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,200
inspect the ancestral hall again.

343
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:58,380
I... I'll go light the candles first.

344
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:07,920
Fei.

345
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,569
What are you doing?

346
00:17:13,109 --> 00:17:14,430
Back in Shiyang,

347
00:17:14,750 --> 00:17:16,810
I saw that the female coroner Cao Hui,

348
00:17:16,810 --> 00:17:17,750
while examining the body,

349
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:18,880
was quite imposing.

350
00:17:19,329 --> 00:17:20,250
I, Physician Fei,

351
00:17:20,250 --> 00:17:21,750
also want to learn and practice.

352
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:23,470
I just touched him

353
00:17:23,490 --> 00:17:24,369
all over,

354
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:25,640
and there were no injuries.

355
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:26,650
The fatal wound

356
00:17:27,150 --> 00:17:28,870
is right at the back of the head.

357
00:17:28,870 --> 00:17:29,750
Step back.

358
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:39,350
Long Tai's judgment was correct.

359
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:42,880
He died from a heavy blow to the back of the head by a heavy object.

360
00:17:43,590 --> 00:17:44,190
A hammer?

361
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:44,950
No

362
00:17:45,630 --> 00:17:46,230
A pickaxe?

363
00:17:46,670 --> 00:17:47,600
Not that either.

364
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:49,550
It should be something

365
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:51,470
like a shovel.

366
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,870
Using a shovel to kill?

367
00:17:54,990 --> 00:17:56,320
Mi Tuo was quite strong.

368
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:57,980
The person who used the shovel

369
00:17:57,980 --> 00:18:00,110
must have considerable arm strength.

370
00:18:13,010 --> 00:18:14,810
I feel like something is missing

371
00:18:14,990 --> 00:18:16,320
in this ancestral hall.

372
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:17,470
What is it?

373
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:19,550
There must be something missing.

374
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:20,870
Xijun is very skilled in painting,

375
00:18:20,870 --> 00:18:22,190
able to remember scenes she sees

376
00:18:22,190 --> 00:18:23,190
and never forget.

377
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:25,120
She shouldn't be mistaken.

378
00:18:25,190 --> 00:18:25,790
But

379
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:27,340
what exactly is it?

380
00:18:29,910 --> 00:18:30,770
I remember now!

381
00:18:31,300 --> 00:18:32,070
It's a pearl.

382
00:18:33,260 --> 00:18:34,540
The pearl

383
00:18:34,710 --> 00:18:36,440
between the statue's fingers.

384
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:38,710
Oh, yes.

385
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:40,490
Mi Tuo

386
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:42,060
even smelled it

387
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:44,690
when he was wiping the statue.

388
00:18:45,030 --> 00:18:45,740
Now that you mention it

389
00:18:45,740 --> 00:18:46,630
I remember too.

390
00:18:46,870 --> 00:18:47,910
There was indeed a pearl.

391
00:18:47,910 --> 00:18:49,630
It was there when Mi Tuo moved in,

392
00:18:49,630 --> 00:18:51,160
but now it has disappeared?

393
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:52,910
Search carefully again.

394
00:18:53,110 --> 00:18:54,150
Yes, look for it.

395
00:18:55,670 --> 00:18:57,230
Where could it have gone?

396
00:19:04,230 --> 00:19:04,830
Su Wuming,

397
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:07,130
why aren't you searching with us?

398
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:08,820
I'm thinking

399
00:19:09,190 --> 00:19:10,990
that this Mi Tuo was a Sogdian,

400
00:19:11,060 --> 00:19:13,070
known for their ability to recognize treasures.

401
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:15,190
Perhaps it was because of this pearl

402
00:19:15,710 --> 00:19:16,740
that he insisted on

403
00:19:16,740 --> 00:19:18,470
living in this ancestral hall.

404
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:19,650
That makes sense.

405
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:32,350
Pearl, oh pearl,

406
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:34,870
who put you here?

407
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:37,780
What a waste of a precious treasure.

408
00:19:37,940 --> 00:19:40,020
Mi Tuo was very cautious.

409
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:42,560
Even when drinking,

410
00:19:42,670 --> 00:19:44,750
he kept his backpack on.

411
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:47,190
It was because

412
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:49,180
of this priceless pearl.

413
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,280
That was why he...

414
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:57,150
So,

415
00:19:57,630 --> 00:20:00,140
Mi Tuo was excited because of getting the pearl

416
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:02,150
and went to the front hall to get wine.

417
00:20:02,150 --> 00:20:05,560
And Lan Juzi took the opportunity to steal his backpack.

418
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:07,550
Well, the murderer...

419
00:20:07,550 --> 00:20:09,510
There were no more footprints in the snow.

420
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,590
The murderer must have been hiding

421
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:12,510
in the ancestral hall for a long time.

422
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:14,340
Who says you have to walk through the snow

423
00:20:14,340 --> 00:20:16,510
to enter the ancestral hall?

424
00:20:19,230 --> 00:20:19,940
Su Wuming,

425
00:20:20,870 --> 00:20:22,110
you reminded me.

426
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:24,470
Xijun,

427
00:20:24,990 --> 00:20:26,870
do you remember when we first entered the ancestral hall

428
00:20:26,870 --> 00:20:28,110
and you said you felt cold?

429
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,640
As soon as I stepped inside,

430
00:20:30,110 --> 00:20:31,830
I felt a chill too.

431
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:35,360
While it's common for ancestral halls

432
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:36,550
to be rundown

433
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:37,990
with leaky roofs,

434
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:39,340
there's something

435
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,390
strange there.

436
00:20:45,360 --> 00:20:46,180
Stay back.

437
00:21:20,640 --> 00:21:21,970
You are doing this because we can't go up there,

438
00:21:21,970 --> 00:21:22,690
right?

439
00:21:23,550 --> 00:21:24,710
What did he see?

440
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:26,870
Yingtao,

441
00:21:27,110 --> 00:21:29,640
why don't you go up there and take a look for us?

442
00:21:30,460 --> 00:21:31,230
No, no, no.

443
00:21:31,950 --> 00:21:33,080
Don't listen to Fei.

444
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:35,140
He's examining the footprints.

445
00:21:35,230 --> 00:21:38,830
If too many people go up there, the footprints will get messed up.

446
00:22:51,150 --> 00:22:53,080
There's a skylight in the second-floor storage room.

447
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:53,940
The murderer must have sneaked into

448
00:22:53,940 --> 00:22:55,200
the top of the ancestral hall from there,

449
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:56,000
then jumped down

450
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,000
and killed Mi Tuo.

451
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:01,430
This person must be very skilled in flying skill.

452
00:23:01,430 --> 00:23:03,960
Although no footprints were left in the snow,

453
00:23:04,790 --> 00:23:06,430
there are rows of footprints on the roof of the ancestral hall

454
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:07,510
and on the roofs

455
00:23:07,530 --> 00:23:08,590
of the wing-rooms.

456
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:10,710
What's suspicious is that,

457
00:23:10,710 --> 00:23:12,860
judging by the size of the footprints,

458
00:23:14,310 --> 00:23:16,310
they were left by different people.

459
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:19,080
Who could they be then?

460
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:21,200
Isn't everyone here?

461
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:29,660
No.

462
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:32,390
No, from the time we entered the shop until now,

463
00:23:32,390 --> 00:23:33,720
two people are missing.

464
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,010
Besides the landlady,

465
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:37,350
there's also the old waiter who ran away.

466
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:38,910
That old waiter

467
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:41,770
must have gone out through the back door, jumped onto the courtyard wall,

468
00:23:41,770 --> 00:23:44,030
entered the forest behind the mountain.

469
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:47,110
And then, when we weren't looking, he returned

470
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,420
and sneaked into the ancestral hall and killed him.

471
00:23:49,420 --> 00:23:50,740
That makes sense.

472
00:23:50,910 --> 00:23:51,590
Because

473
00:23:52,070 --> 00:23:53,680
he knew

474
00:23:53,710 --> 00:23:56,170
that Mi Tuo was living in the ancestral hall.

475
00:23:56,630 --> 00:23:57,310
However,

476
00:23:58,670 --> 00:24:00,550
there's another possibility.

477
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:05,780
Tying the red ribbon

478
00:24:05,780 --> 00:24:07,190
was probably a way

479
00:24:07,230 --> 00:24:08,670
to tell the accomplice outside

480
00:24:08,670 --> 00:24:10,650
that someone was living in the inn.

481
00:24:11,190 --> 00:24:12,630
When the accomplice came back

482
00:24:12,630 --> 00:24:13,990
and saw the red ribbon,

483
00:24:14,020 --> 00:24:16,710
he went around to the forest behind the mountain.

484
00:24:16,710 --> 00:24:20,640
Then he jumped over the courtyard wall and entered the ancestral hall.

485
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:24,470
That's so creepy.

486
00:24:24,620 --> 00:24:26,480
And the other row of footprints

487
00:24:26,950 --> 00:24:29,740
is even more terrifying.

488
00:24:30,430 --> 00:24:32,020
Swordsman was right.

489
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:37,030
Everyone alive is here.

490
00:24:37,510 --> 00:24:38,630
Unless...

491
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:52,130
Unless the landlady came back to life.

492
00:24:58,120 --> 00:24:59,710
The landlady is dead?

493
00:25:02,630 --> 00:25:04,160
It was before you came here.

494
00:25:04,990 --> 00:25:07,120
There was another murder before this,

495
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:09,350
and you deliberately concealed it?

496
00:25:10,190 --> 00:25:11,670
Come on, Long.

497
00:25:11,870 --> 00:25:13,470
Do you still think you're a sheriff?

498
00:25:13,470 --> 00:25:13,830
I...

499
00:25:14,070 --> 00:25:15,870
Come on, get him down.

500
00:25:16,710 --> 00:25:17,750
Open the tank.

501
00:25:26,670 --> 00:25:27,750
The rope is intact.

502
00:25:29,710 --> 00:25:30,350
Yingtao.

503
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:49,280
Where is him?

504
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:50,310
Well...

505
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,090
Where is the corpse?

506
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:57,820
Then there must be something wrong with this tank.

507
00:25:57,820 --> 00:26:00,020
While playing with the Tokhara knives,

508
00:26:00,780 --> 00:26:03,510
the lid of this large tank was open the whole time.

509
00:26:04,630 --> 00:26:05,390
Perhaps

510
00:26:06,610 --> 00:26:07,980
it's a place that the landlady

511
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:08,860
intentionally left for herself

512
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,790
to hide her body.

513
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,770
Your analysis is correct.

514
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:14,470
Perhaps this is the truth.

515
00:26:16,390 --> 00:26:17,390
Let me take a look.

516
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:33,500
Yingtao, be careful.

517
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:35,240
Don't worry.

518
00:26:43,950 --> 00:26:45,510
Fortunately, there's this girl.

519
00:26:45,510 --> 00:26:47,510
The entrance of the hole is so narrow.

520
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:48,350
We men

521
00:26:48,470 --> 00:26:50,000
simply cannot fit through.

522
00:26:59,430 --> 00:27:00,590
There's no dust inside the cave.

523
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:01,670
The walls are smooth.

524
00:27:01,670 --> 00:27:04,330
It seems that someone crawls in here regularly.

525
00:27:04,980 --> 00:27:06,240
If I'm not mistaken,

526
00:27:06,630 --> 00:27:08,640
that landlady must have taken some medicine

527
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:10,270
to temporarily stop her breath.

528
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:11,400
That can't be right.

529
00:27:11,630 --> 00:27:12,750
I saw the dagger piercing into her chest

530
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,780
with my own eyes.

531
00:27:15,150 --> 00:27:16,190
We were so close.

532
00:27:16,790 --> 00:27:17,790
The blood was...

533
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:19,390
Hermit Jiang,

534
00:27:19,670 --> 00:27:21,600
it even stained all over your hand.

535
00:27:27,230 --> 00:27:29,030
All these are just petty tricks.

536
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:30,070
Attach two blood packs separately

537
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:31,350
to the chest and back.

538
00:27:31,670 --> 00:27:32,790
Use the Tokhara knife to squeeze,

539
00:27:32,790 --> 00:27:34,350
and the blood will come out.

540
00:27:36,980 --> 00:27:38,980
Now, the most important thing is...

541
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:40,670
The most important thing

542
00:27:40,670 --> 00:27:42,490
is that we can't keep living in this inn.

543
00:27:42,490 --> 00:27:42,970
It's...

544
00:27:44,150 --> 00:27:46,430
As Fei just said,

545
00:27:47,050 --> 00:27:48,180
if she took medicine

546
00:27:48,210 --> 00:27:50,010
to temporarily stop her breath,

547
00:27:50,890 --> 00:27:52,450
she could wake up later

548
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:55,550
and use this underground passage

549
00:27:55,550 --> 00:27:57,710
to crawl out from behind the counter.

550
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:04,180
Then, when no one was paying attention,

551
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,870
she could go upstairs

552
00:28:06,990 --> 00:28:09,870
and get onto the roof of the ancestral hall

553
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:13,790
through the skylight in the storeroom.

554
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:15,880
It was she who killed Mi Tuo?

555
00:28:15,990 --> 00:28:17,630
But because I arrived in time,

556
00:28:17,630 --> 00:28:19,350
she didn't have time to hide the corpse.

557
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:20,750
That's possible.

558
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:24,590
But from Mi Tuo returning to the ancestral hall

559
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:25,740
with food and drink,

560
00:28:25,870 --> 00:28:26,730
to being killed,

561
00:28:26,730 --> 00:28:28,750
and then to the body being discovered,

562
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,080
the time was very short.

563
00:28:31,550 --> 00:28:33,990
Where could the landlady

564
00:28:34,030 --> 00:28:36,030
who committed the murder be hiding?

565
00:28:38,790 --> 00:28:40,890
When we were expressing our feelings in the snow,

566
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:43,090
did you hear the sound?

567
00:28:44,910 --> 00:28:45,770
Who's in there?

568
00:28:45,990 --> 00:28:46,590
Come out!

569
00:28:47,990 --> 00:28:48,720
Come out now!

570
00:28:52,590 --> 00:28:54,670
I heard it very clearly.

571
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:57,880
It did come from the direction of the ancestral hall.

572
00:28:58,470 --> 00:28:59,800
Now that I think about it

573
00:29:00,390 --> 00:29:02,400
that sound was not from

574
00:29:02,420 --> 00:29:03,950
inside the ancestral hall,

575
00:29:04,000 --> 00:29:05,440
but from underneath it.

576
00:29:33,030 --> 00:29:34,470
There seems to be a hollow sound underground,

577
00:29:34,470 --> 00:29:36,130
but I didn't find an entrance.

578
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:42,190
This Mo's Inn

579
00:29:42,230 --> 00:29:44,790
is really deceiving people with false appearances.

