867
00:42:58,680 --> 00:43:00,320
My master is kind-hearted

868
00:43:00,850 --> 00:43:02,450
and doesn't want to kill you!

869
00:43:03,190 --> 00:43:03,990
What a pity.

870
00:43:04,500 --> 00:43:05,580
Even playing with the Tokhara knife

871
00:43:05,580 --> 00:43:06,980
couldn't scare you away.

872
00:43:07,550 --> 00:43:09,350
I have no choice but to be a bad guy

873
00:43:09,540 --> 00:43:11,230
and send you to hell.

874
00:43:14,270 --> 00:43:14,790
Oh no,

875
00:43:15,330 --> 00:43:16,990
the retreat route is blocked.

876
00:43:17,160 --> 00:43:18,870
It sounds like the old waiter.

877
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:20,790
Those at the top, hurry and fight your way back.

878
00:43:20,790 --> 00:43:23,310
He's alone, so he shouldn't be hard to deal with.

879
00:43:23,310 --> 00:43:24,550
It's too late.

880
00:43:25,580 --> 00:43:26,830
Haven't you noticed?

881
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:29,480
The stairs are covered in copper oil.

882
00:43:30,150 --> 00:43:32,210
He's planning to attack us with fire.

883
00:43:36,520 --> 00:43:37,580
Don't make a sound,

884
00:43:38,070 --> 00:43:39,400
to avoid alerting them.

885
00:43:39,580 --> 00:43:40,670
It's cramped here,

886
00:43:41,340 --> 00:43:42,600
if there's fire above,

887
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:45,420
we'll definitely be burned to death.

888
00:43:46,440 --> 00:43:47,830
What should we do?
